{
  "id": "69ee95387693418d7e137671",
  "title": "良い意見かどうかは1人だと中々わからないので、とりあえず言ってみたほうが良い",
  "created": 1777243452,
  "updated": 1777271481,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69ee95387693418d7e137671",
      "text": "良い意見かどうかは1人だと中々わからないので、とりあえず言ってみたほうが良い",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777243452,
      "updated": 1777243452
    },
    {
      "id": "69ee95720000000000141a3c",
      "text": " 良い意見でも、そうでなくても、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777243506,
      "updated": 1777268781
    },
    {
      "id": "69eee98200000000000c8826",
      "text": " とりあえず言ってみたほうが良い",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777265027,
      "updated": 1777268781
    },
    {
      "id": "69eee98400000000000c8827",
      "text": " 価値判断をするのは読者",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777265028,
      "updated": 1777268781
    },
    {
      "id": "69eef81000000000000c8835",
      "text": "  [フィルターは各自がやればいい]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777268752,
      "updated": 1777269415
    },
    {
      "id": "69eef82000000000000c8836",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777268769,
      "updated": 1777268769
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeb711000000000056e77d",
      "text": "[考えながらまとめる]（空ページ）を実行してみました",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777252113,
      "updated": 1777269488
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeb31300000000002998a1",
      "text": "空ページは[suto3.icon]の思考の邪魔をする要素なのだが、今回はあえて書いている",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777251091,
      "updated": 1777267264
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeb4a100000000002998a6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777251490,
      "updated": 1777251490
    },
    {
      "id": "69eee92100000000000c8822",
      "text": "良い意見、良いアイデア",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777264929,
      "updated": 1777268798
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeec8200000000000c8828",
      "text": "　良い意見とは",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777265795,
      "updated": 1777265802
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeec9b00000000000c882a",
      "text": "　　「良い」意味するところは多義",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777265820,
      "updated": 1777265844
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeee9700000000004381b5",
      "text": "　　よくわからない",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777266327,
      "updated": 1777266327
    },
    {
      "id": "69eef84300000000000c8837",
      "text": "　良いアイデアとは",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777268804,
      "updated": 1777268809
    },
    {
      "id": "69eee92100000000000c8823",
      "text": " 　[小さいアイデアのかけらの扱い方]（空ページ）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777264929,
      "updated": 1777268816
    },
    {
      "id": "69eee92100000000000c8824",
      "text": " 　[良いアイデアは勝手に育つ、他人が育ててくれるから]（空ページ）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777264929,
      "updated": 1777268817
    },
    {
      "id": "69eee92500000000000c8825",
      "text": "　　よくわからない",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777264933,
      "updated": 1777269205
    },
    {
      "id": "69eef9d300000000002fa392",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777269203,
      "updated": 1777269203
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeb1d6000000000056e773",
      "text": "[意見]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777250774,
      "updated": 1777264933
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeb31200000000002998a0",
      "text": " [声の大きい意見]（空ページ）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777251090,
      "updated": 1777267325
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeb31f00000000002998a2",
      "text": " [少数意見]（空ページ）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777251103,
      "updated": 1777267334
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeb37500000000002998a3",
      "text": " [意見の押し付け]（空ページ）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777251190,
      "updated": 1777267346
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeb39800000000002998a4",
      "text": " [意見の対立]（空ページ）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777251225,
      "updated": 1777267365
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeb3ad00000000002998a5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777251245,
      "updated": 1777251245
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeb21e000000000056e776",
      "text": "[自分の意見]（空ページ）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777250847,
      "updated": 1777267373
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeb225000000000056e778",
      "text": " [自分の意見と他者の意見とを分離する]（空ページ）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777250853,
      "updated": 1777267382
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeb239000000000056e779",
      "text": " [自分の意見を吟味]（空ページ）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777250874,
      "updated": 1777267393
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeb247000000000056e77a",
      "text": " [人の発言を待たずに自分の意見を書ける]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777250888,
      "updated": 1777250925
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeb220000000000056e777",
      "text": " [自分の意見にはアイコンつけて欲しい]（空ページ）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777250849,
      "updated": 1777267448
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeb252000000000056e77b",
      "text": " [自分の意見がない]（空ページ）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777250898,
      "updated": 1777267458
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeb25d000000000056e77c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777250910,
      "updated": 1777250910
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeb14a000000000056e76d",
      "text": "意見を言う",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777250635,
      "updated": 1777250654
    },
    {
      "id": "69eef13a00000000000c882b",
      "text": " [言い方の問題]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777267002,
      "updated": 1777267016
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeb186000000000056e770",
      "text": " [意見を表明するのが苦手]（空ページ）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777250694,
      "updated": 1777267481
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeb14b000000000056e76e",
      "text": " [自分の意見を吟味]（空ページ）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777250635,
      "updated": 1777267488
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeb15f000000000056e76f",
      "text": " [書き込まれた意見を大胆に編集]（空ページ）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777250656,
      "updated": 1777267506
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeb2f5000000000029989f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777251062,
      "updated": 1777251062
    },
    {
      "id": "69eecb52000000000037cdcb",
      "text": "とりあえず言ってみる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777257298,
      "updated": 1777257310
    },
    {
      "id": "69eecb53000000000037cdcc",
      "text": " [嫌なことを表明するのが良いという文化]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777257300,
      "updated": 1777257420
    },
    {
      "id": "69eecbcb000000000037cdce",
      "text": " [とりあえずやってみる] - [とりあえずやってみて]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777257420,
      "updated": 1777257436
    },
    {
      "id": "69eecbdb000000000037cdcf",
      "text": " [教え合える環境] - [教え合える環境でない環境]（空ページ）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777257436,
      "updated": 1777267794
    },
    {
      "id": "69eed09b000000000037cdd0",
      "text": "　[アホな質問をたくさんするぞ〜]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777258651,
      "updated": 1777269244
    },
    {
      "id": "69eef9fb00000000002fa393",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777269244,
      "updated": 1777269244
    },
    {
      "id": "69eee66300000000004381b1",
      "text": "言わなければわからない",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777264228,
      "updated": 1777264249
    },
    {
      "id": "69eee83800000000000c880c",
      "text": " [意思表示]として",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777264696,
      "updated": 1777269376
    },
    {
      "id": "69eee66300000000004381b2",
      "text": "　[言わざるを得ない]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777264228,
      "updated": 1777264335
    },
    {
      "id": "69eee83200000000000c880b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777264690,
      "updated": 1777264817
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeaf99000000000056e761",
      "text": "[敷居を下げる]（空ページ）、ハードルを下げる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777250202,
      "updated": 1777267932
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeb02b000000000056e764",
      "text": " [Scrapboxを書く敷居を下げる]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777250347,
      "updated": 1777250418
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeb04d000000000056e765",
      "text": " [書く敷居を下げる]（空ページ）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777250382,
      "updated": 1777267951
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeb051000000000056e766",
      "text": " [くだらないことや未完成の内容を書いて敷居を下げ]る",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777250386,
      "updated": 1777264958
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeb055000000000056e767",
      "text": " [書くための敷居を削]（空ページ）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777250390,
      "updated": 1777268106
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeafff000000000056e763",
      "text": " [しょーもないことを書いてハードル下げる]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777250304,
      "updated": 1777250308
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeb09b000000000056e768",
      "text": " [書くハードル]（空ページ） - [聞くハードル]（空ページ） - [様々なハードル]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777250459,
      "updated": 1777268164
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeb0cd000000000056e76b",
      "text": "　[やり方を忘れてハードルが上が]る（空ページ）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777250510,
      "updated": 1777268207
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeb123000000000056e76c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777250595,
      "updated": 1777250595
    },
    {
      "id": "69eef78300000000000c8833",
      "text": "[価値判断]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777268612,
      "updated": 1777271481
    },
    {
      "id": "69eef6c400000000000c882f",
      "text": "　[価値が無い]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777268420,
      "updated": 1777271481
    },
    {
      "id": "69eef6c500000000000c8830",
      "text": " [被リンク数の多いページは本当に価値が高いのか]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777268421,
      "updated": 1777271481
    },
    {
      "id": "69eef6dc00000000000c8831",
      "text": " [価値ある情報]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777268445,
      "updated": 1777271481
    },
    {
      "id": "69eef7ac00000000000c8834",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777268652,
      "updated": 1777269428
    },
    {
      "id": "69eeaf99000000000056e762",
      "text": "他、参考ページ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777250202,
      "updated": 1777271476
    },
    {
      "id": "69eead44000000000056e75f",
      "text": " [自転車置場の議論]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777249605,
      "updated": 1777271476
    },
    {
      "id": "69ee953c0000000000141a39",
      "text": " [有意義なことに絞って書こうとしてしまいがち]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777243452,
      "updated": 1777271476
    },
    {
      "id": "69ee953d0000000000141a3a",
      "text": " [書く前に自重vs書いてからフィルター]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777243453,
      "updated": 1777271476
    },
    {
      "id": "69ee958e0000000000141a3d",
      "text": " [アウトプットは量多い方がいい。フィルタは各自がやればいい。この原則わかんない奴はインターネット合わないと思う。]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777243534,
      "updated": 1777271476
    },
    {
      "id": "69ee96500000000000af536e",
      "text": " [あなたにしか役に立たない情報]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777243729,
      "updated": 1777271476
    },
    {
      "id": "69ee973a0000000000907c7a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777243963,
      "updated": 1777269238
    }
  ]
}